After having agreed to the grant application, the directors participated in several meetings with Saint-Etienne Métropole and the State, to determine the actions that will be highlighted in the documentary entitled «Towards the social link». The first phase of the project was to contact all the associative structures working within the framework of the political actions of the city, to study their actions and objectives, and to schedule with them, the dates of shooting. Seven structures were selected. (Social center Sous-Paulat de Firminy - Forezien roof and social center of Saint-Paul in Jarez - Carnage Company, Rive de Gier - Local Misson Forez, Andrézieux Bouthéon - Collective X, Saint-Etienne - Contemporary Ballet Mireille BARLET, Saint-Etienne - Kaleidoscope, Conseil Citoyen, Saint-Etienne) The criteria for the selection of projects were: - State of progress of their project - Diversity of the contents of the actions - Geographical diversity of the structures - Visual relevance of the project The choice of structures was validated by the financers»'}, {'Режиссер': [['Dominique Dozolme', '/name/5140098/'], ['Farid Milaz', '/name/6110088/']]}, {'Сценарий': [['Dominique Dozolme', '/name/5140098/'], ['Farid Milaz', '/name/6110088/']]}, {'Продюсер': [['Farid Milaz', '/name/6110088/'], ['Jean-Claude Parayre', '/name/6110090/']]}, {'Композитор': '—'}, {'Монтаж': [['Dominique Dozolme', '/name/5140098/']]}, {'Время': '23 мин.'}], [{'actor_name': 'Amandine Brenier', 'link': '/name/6110089/'}], ['none', 'none', 'none']]
